OL,3,CNHS launch major new campaign for 10-
OL,4,Cminute lifesaving screening
OL,6,FA dad-of-two who was resuscitated
OL,7,Fafter having a ruptured abdominal
OL,8,Faortic aneurism (AAA) has backed a
OL,9,Fmajor new NHS campaign to raise
OL,10,Fawareness of life-saving screening.
OL,12,FIan Bythell, a dad-of-two from
OL,13,FRoughlee in Pendle was diagnosed with
OL,14,Fa ruptured AAA in October 2024.
OL,16,FAAA is a deadly bulge in the aorta,
OL,17,Fthe largest artery in the body, that
OL,18,Fif it bursts can kill more than 80 per
OL,19,Fcent of the people who have it if it
OL,20,Fis left untreated.
