OL,3,CNHS launch major new campaign for 10-
OL,4,Cminute lifesaving screening
OL,6,FAfter feeling unwell and collapsing at
OL,7,Fhome, he was rushed to the Royal
OL,8,FBlackburn Teaching Hospital, where he
OL,9,Fwas immediately admitted to the
OL,10,Fresuscitation ward.
OL,12,FA fast scan revealed the ruptured AAA,
OL,13,Fbut before Ian could get to theatre
OL,14,Ffor emergency surgery he went into
OL,15,Fcardiac arrest.
OL,17,FIt took medics more than 40 minutes of
OL,18,Fchest compressions to resuscitate Ian,
OL,19,Fand then a further eight hours in
OL,20,Fsurgery to repair the damage to the
OL,21,Faorta.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
