OL,3,CNHS launch major new campaign for 10-
OL,4,Cminute lifesaving screening
OL,6,FIan's wife Deb, and their two
OL,7,Fdaughters Liv and Freya were able to
OL,8,Fgo and sit with him following the
OL,9,Fsurgery, but Ian was heavily sedated
OL,10,Fand on a ventilator.
OL,12,FHowever, miraculously, the following
OL,13,Fday Ian had come around, and because
OL,14,Fhis voice was strained from the
OL,15,Fventilator, he was making hand
OL,16,Fmovements to ask clinicians if he was
OL,17,Fable to walk and ski.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
