OL,3,CNHS launch major new campaign for 10-
OL,4,Cminute lifesaving screening
OL,6,FAlmost six-weeks later, on 10
OL,7,FDecember, and just in time for
OL,8,FChristmas, Ian was fit for discharge
OL,9,Fand allowed home.
OL,11,FIan said: "Every bit of my care has
OL,12,Fbeen absolutely phenomenal, and as a
OL,13,Ffamily we can't thank everyone enough.
OL,15,F"I had no idea before this happened to
OL,16,Fme what AAA was, and I hope this
OL,17,Fcampaign makes more people aware of
OL,18,Fthe dangers and the importance of the
OL,19,Fscreening programme."
