OL,3,CNHS launch major new campaign for 10-
OL,4,Cminute lifesaving screening
OL,6,FThe NHS campaign is calling on men
OL,7,Fover the age of 65 to take a 10 minute
OL,8,Ftest to check for Abdominal Aortic
OL,9,FAneurysms (AAA).
OL,11,FThe 10-minute, pain free scan of the
OL,12,Fabdomen can be done at your local GP
OL,13,For hospital and will detect any
OL,14,Fswelling early, reduce the chances of
OL,15,Frupture, and save lives.
OL,17,FIn the year leading up to April 2024,
OL,18,Fonly 78.9% of men in the North West
OL,19,Fattended a screening appointment
OL,20,Fwithin the year they were invited.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
