OL,6,FTricia Spedding, Head of Public Health
OL,7,Ffor NHS England North West, said: "Of
OL,8,Fall the screening programmes the NHS
OL,9,Foffers, AAA screening is the least
OL,10,Fwell known, and yet the risk of an
OL,11,Fundetected and untreated AAA is one of
OL,12,Fthe most deadly.
