OL,3,CNHS launch major new campaign for 10-
OL,4,Cminute lifesaving screening
OL,6,F"We hope this brand-new campaign
OL,7,Fraises awareness of AAA screening
OL,8,Facross the North West, not just with
OL,9,Fmen aged 65-and-over, but also with
OL,10,Fyounger men who will eventually be
OL,11,Fcalled for screening, and with friends
OL,12,Fand family, who can support their
OL,13,Floved ones to come forward for their
OL,14,FAAA check.
OL,16,F"The scan is completely painless, and
OL,17,Fif there is no aneurysm detected, you
OL,18,Fdon't need to have any more scans and
OL,19,Fif we do detect an aneurysm, it can be
OL,20,Ftreated early and monitored.
